(173, 1, '2016-10-27 04:23:44', '2016-10-27 04:23:44', '\n\nAbout								\n																						We do the research so you don&#8217;t have to\n\n\n\n<!-- .container -->\n								 <!-- .overlay -->\n\nWhy we do what we do																											\n																																					First of all, we are average guys just like you. &nbsp;One thing we all have in common is our relationships have all gone through some rough patches. &nbsp;Facing divorce, humiliation, loneliness and f*#king up our kids we banded together and started to researching the best way to get our relationships back on track.We soon figured out that there was a lot of bulls#*t out there advice wise, but through applying the 80/20 principle we started to stumble upon some nuggets of gold (the 20% that produces the 80% of the results) that brought our relationships back from the brink.&nbsp;This site is about distilling the art of relationship maintenance into easy automated systems so that we guys we will do it. &nbsp;We have read the books and the brain science so your don&#8217;t have to. Just join the crew and get the results.\n\n<!-- /row -->\n\nJoin the Crew									\n																									As a member of our site you will get access to some pretty awesome automated tools and reminders that will help you get easy results in your relationship. We are always testing out new strategies and methods and as a member you will get the inside scoop and can even take part testing this stuff out on your wife and reaping the sweet rewards.\n\n<a href="#buy-more">\n									Join Now								</a>\n\n', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '41-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-10-27 04:23:44', '2016-10-27 04:23:44', 'a:4:{s:7:"post_id";i:41;s:9:"post_hash";s:44:"layers_page_25e67f69a617f2b22d2d7fe1976db063";s:10:"post_title";s:5:"About";s:11:"widget_data";a:1:{s:22:"obox-layers-builder-41";a:5:{s:23:"layers-widget-column-13";a:4:{s:6:"design";a:7:{s:6:"layout";s:12:"layout-boxed";s:9:"liststyle";s: